  "description": "Non-Material Amendment Application under Section 96A of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended) to introduce the phased delivery (phases 0-3) of planning permission reference 71374/APP/2016/4027, dated 29-07-19, for the demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to provide a podium at ground level and buildings ranging from four storeys to nine storeys, comprising 122 residential units (Class C3) and 230sqm of flexible commercial space (Use Classes A1, A3, B1, D1 or D2), together with associated car parking, vehicular access, landscaping, infrastructure works and the extension of Shackles Dock.",
